Gevyn vnder oure signet at Edynburgh ye xii day of Januar, and of our regne the xv yher. Quibus carta regia et littera perlectis prouidus vir Robertus de Balmando burgensis burgi de Dunde prelocutor prepositi bal- liuorum et consilii dicti burgi ex parte eorundem publice protestabatur incon- tinenter post lecturam dictarum carte et littere sic dicendo in lingua vulgari. .We protest that sen we ar feft of kyngis of this realme vith bovndis ancl fredomys as ovr feftmentis and charteris proportis in thaim self that this pre· tendit feftment to Brechyn, pvrchest of fals suggestioun be informatiouu os partiale personys contrar the infeftmentis and preuilegis of kyngis of this realme in preiudice of the kyngis fe and heritage and ovris, turn vs nor our infeftmentis to na preiudice na skathe in tyme to cum, gif we be law may hafe remede tharof.
